WEBVTT

1
00:14:06.750 --> 00:14:09.500 
就像你对我的所作所为一样吗
You mean the same courtesy you've extended me?

2
00:14:09.500 --> 00:14:12.810 
你的委员会在调查总统  参议员
Your committee is investigating the President, Senator.

3
00:14:12.810 --> 00:14:15.850 
这根本不是一码事  白宫也没有人
It is hardly the same thing. Nobody at the White House

4
00:14:15.850 --> 00:14:18.820 
在为难你的妻子和孩子
is impugning your wife or your children.

5
00:14:18.820 --> 00:14:21.140 
我只是在跟着证据走
I'm only following the evidence where it leads.

6
00:14:21.140 --> 00:14:23.040 
证据  什么证据
Evidence? What evidence?

7
00:14:23.490 --> 00:14:26.230 
她只是个普通公民
This is a civilian we're talking about.

8
00:14:26.230 --> 00:14:29.340 
她根本就不在此事的调查范围内
She is so far outside the scope of the inquiry,

9
00:14:29.340 --> 00:14:30.990 
简直可笑
it is laughable.

10
00:14:31.280 --> 00:14:34.390 
我想你没有自己以为的那样了解她
I don't think you know her as well as you think you do.

11
00:14:35.340 --> 00:14:37.180 
这话又是什么意思
And what's that supposed to mean?

12
00:14:37.410 --> 00:14:39.640 
我想明天我们就知道了  不是吗
I guess we'll find out tomorrow, won't we?

